# DESCRIPTION
# Convert an ellipse from polar to cartesian coordinates and find distances from the pole to the vertices.
#
# ENDDESCRIPTION
## DBsubject(Algebra)
## DBchapter(Conic sections)
## DBsection(Polar or parametric form)
## Institution(John Wiley & sons)
## MO(1)
## TitleText1('Calculus')
